<feature
      id="com.hudren.woodpile"
      label="Woodpile"
      version="0.7"
      provider-name="Hudren Andromeda Connection"
      plugin="com.hudren.woodpile">

   <description>
      Woodpile is an Eclipse plugin for capturing and viewing Apache
Log4j events. 
Inspired by Chainsaw. 
Intended for developers. 
Requires Eclipse 3.5 and JDK 1.6 runtime. 
Compatible with Log4j 1.2.17 and Log4j2 2.0 beta9.
Uses Beanshell 2.0b4.
   </description>

